text: Lee Sung-jin (born March 7, 1985) is a South Korean archer. Lee competed at the 2004 Summer Olympics and the 2012 Summer Olympics.Lee Seong-JinSung Jin LEE ==References== Category:1985 births Category:Living people Category:South Korean archers Category:Olympic gold medalists for South Korea Category:Olympic silver medalists for South Korea
